S.FORM: Azerbaijan Gaga kska Yacow ka Azerbaijan, 40 30 N, 47 30 E ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 86,600 sq km(hangan na o Tg113) (knlbanga dxgal o 82,629 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 3,971 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 9,872,765 hiyi. Gaga Baku ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 28 idas 5 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Azerbaijan ga wada sugan 57.60 ka dxgal qpahan, 11.30 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 31.10 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Ilham Aliyev, pnaah hngkawas2003 idas 10 jiyax 31pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
